SnowCat::

She saw the rocket come towards her.  She waited, then at the last 
second, jumped to the side to get out of the way.  The rocket struck 
ground near her.  She fell and slowly got up.  She started off again 
towards Striker and Ramulus. She fired her optic lazars at Striker. 
Ignoring her side, wires exposed and flapping around as she ran.
